## Installing GrayWolf Plugin

1. Copy plugin directory to plugins folder:
   cp -r graywolf/ /path/to/ham_radio_app/plugins/implementations/

2. Restart the application:
   docker-compose restart app

3. Navigate to GrayWolf in the Plugins menu.

4. On first load, click Install GrayWolf if not auto-installed.

5. Configure your callsign and settings.

6. Click Start GrayWolf to connect.